/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "C_BoothDeductionArea" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "C_BoothDeductionArea"
(
ID NUMBER(32) not null,
"BoothID" NUMBER(32),
"FacilityID" NUMBER(32),
"DeductionArea" DECIMAL(20, 4),
"StartTime" TIMESTAMP,
"EndTime" TIMESTAMP,
"Enable" INTEGER,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32),
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP,
"ModifyBy" NUMBER(32),
"ModifyTime" TIMESTAMP,
constraint PK_C_BOOTHDEDUCTIONAREA primary key (ID)
);

comment on column "C_BoothDeductionArea"."Enable" is
'1：启用
0：停用';

alter table "C_BoothDeductionArea"

references "C_Booth" ("BoothID");

alter table "C_BoothDeductionArea"
add constraint FK_C_BDA_2_C_DF_PK foreign key ("FacilityID")
references "C_DeductionFacility" ("FacilityID");
